{"tid":1433012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]一邊放人一邊搜屋！警方釋放方仲賢前30分鐘拉隊到其位於西貢的住所搜查","createTime":"2019-08-08T11:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T13:30:09.000Z","uid":46640,"like":77,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f4b54d57b9bf0cb1a1a958a2098407f223401ed2","tid":1433012,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:21:24.000Z","msg":"男公關收到獨家消息，警方看似在晚上6時釋放方仲賢，但原來警方早在17時30分拉大隊到其位於西貢的住宅入屋搜索，搜索時間由17時30分至19時左右，搜屋時間長逾1小時。<br />\n<br />\n早有消息向男公關透露，警隊這次以「攻擊性武器」罪拘捕在街上的方仲賢，其實旨在向法庭申請搜查令入屋，最後搞出SSP狂放催淚彈的大龍鳯。<br />\n<br />\n而家係咪要講推上連登好過推上報？<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2391563511125393&amp;id=1648246202123798\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2391563511125393%26id%3D1648246202123798&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9Qg0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=98df179e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2391563511125393&amp;id=1648246202123798</a>"},{"pid":"d35ac9915a2b56897fc7e40c5b1eb7e09324c6af","tid":1433012,"uid":36478,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:22:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68d5813427b40c764feb4d730d9b02fdc82e45d","tid":1433012,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:22:13.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d549124d22a846d34a57a87cb358e9cafaa2ffd","tid":1433012,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"10 連推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1882c70894ef738b59295cdcf03c59e1533c92c6","tid":1433012,"uid":46640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T11:23:12.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e093b00230056d87416f748cd76087b3285ab2be","tid":